  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate", 
    "date": "2017-11-16T05:00:00Z", 
    "text": "CHP Support Act\n\nThis bill amends the Energy Policy and Conservation Act to redesignate the Department of Energy's Clean Energy Application Centers as the CHP Technical Assistance Partnership Program. The program must encourage deployment of combined heat and power technologies and provide project specific support to building and industrial professionals through economic and engineering assessments and advisory activities. This bill reauthorizes the program through FY2022."
